Functional Requirements
Allow user to:
•	Set weekly budgets
•	Add payments
•	view remaining budget for week
•	save payees
•	search past payments
o	by payee
o	by time period
Non-Functional Requirements
•	Display remaining budget in green text when it’s at least 2/3rds of the weekly budget
•	Display remaining budget in amber text when it’s at least 1/3rd and less than 2/3rds of the weekly budget
•	Display remaining budget in red text when it’s less than 1/3rd of the weekly budget
•	Display dates in the format dd/mm/yyyy
•	Display time in the 24hr digital format hh:mm

